{"tid":446726,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《明報》又出錯　扶貧變「扶貪」","createTime":"2017-10-24T14:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T03:54:03.000Z","uid":5195,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cd1202e92e198a6c45539d7cc701fc6cec9a089a","tid":446726,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:37:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171024/bkn-20171024192827143-1024_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171024%2Fbkn-20171024192827143-1024_00822_001.html&d=BE8umleqyV4iKsUKwd3M45UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=48458d5b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171024/bkn-20171024192827143-1024_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n一度自詡「公信第一」的《明報》，過往報道曾多次出錯，本年至今，已有64則新聞須刊登「更正與澄清」。其中，該報於本月20日刊登的一篇文章中，便把「扶貧」寫成「扶貪」，鬧出笑話。<br />\n<br />\n《明報》於10月20日刊登一篇有關中共總書記習近平，參加中共十九大貴州省代表團討論的報道時，文章小題誤寫成「可提拔『溫室』青年到扶貪一線練一練」，被不少讀者恥笑。《明報》於翌日刊登「更正與澄清」，並於網站上更正，把「扶貪」改成「扶貧」。<br />\n<br />\n自2000年初起，《明報》一直於報頭印上「公信力第一」字眼，其理據部分來自中文大學傳播與民意調查中心進行的本地新聞機構公信力調查。不過，《明報》於該調查的公信力排名持續下滑，排名於2014年由第2位下跌至第3位，最終「跪低」刪去「公信第一」字眼；而於去年的最新調查當中，《明報》仍維持第3位。"},{"pid":"245cb756e448e1e369483ad7c4f039ad9676f6cc","tid":446726,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:38:23.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"766987e88d5f4c8865c55e0823bfe5e378cf4c3d","tid":446726,"uid":52942,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:39:05.000Z","msg":"出岩呀，邊有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fbc16334b8902da424f71155285400bb36bc1e8","tid":446726,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:39:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出岩呀，邊有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20171020/tcaa2_r.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Fvan%2Fhtm%2FNews%2F20171020%2Ftcaa2_r.htm&d=BE8umleqyV4iKsUKwd3M45UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=7934c84e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20171020/tcaa2_r.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n可提拔「溫室」青年到扶貪一線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n習近平在發言中肯定了貴州5年來的工作，他又問農民一年交多少保險費，貧困戶生活有沒有改善等，「現在的戰場，重中之重就是扶貧第一線」，他要求關心、愛護扶貧幹部，有條件的話要提拔使用，同時要鼓勵青年幹部到扶貧第一線去，「溫室裏成長的那些(幹部提拔)慢一點，或者到這些(貧困)地方練一練，看看是不是能脫穎而出，賞罰要鮮明」。"},{"pid":"6a87a39bd8869e309295189fc0e1456af70d9927","tid":446726,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:40:01.000Z","msg":"鬼拍後尾枕"},{"pid":"18fa7528f5cc87f6116bfa24fbff00ca52e651bd","tid":446726,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:40:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94adb9587a2de4a9858cbb8f395ae50ea19fa26a","tid":446726,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:41:48.000Z","msg":"東方一年報因航都唔止64次啦"},{"pid":"23e172066cc38b33f2bc39fb7e90f2d55f613fdd","tid":446726,"uid":76488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:43:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ec1eaaaa1bd4bd5bce62291ecbb42cc9b62dcfa","tid":446726,"uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:45:41.000Z","msg":"一度自詡「公信第一」的《明報》, 簡稱&quot;一報&quot;? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac14d4f1051c0f558b8570975349900cc1876ec7","tid":446726,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T15:00:22.000Z","msg":"直插紅心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39aafebddabd727fab99b5f0ba4bd2a55040cc7b","tid":446726,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T15:01:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82651016e5f644ad172b20dba74f1847855